      "sc:citation": {
        "@id": "https://doi.org/10.12688/hrbopenres.13476.2"
      },
      "sc:contributor": "Marcel Ramos",
      "sc:description": "GNOSIS incorporates a range of R packages enabling users to efficiently explore and visualise clinical and genomic data obtained from cBioPortal. GNOSIS uses an intuitive GUI and multiple tab panels supporting a range of functionalities. These include data upload and initial exploration, data recoding and subsetting, multiple visualisations, survival analysis, statistical analysis and mutation analysis, in addition to facilitating reproducible research.",
